ity Battle: The Siege of Berlin<br /><br />PART VI: THE WAR IN THE PACIFIC 1943-1945<br />Chapter 29: Roosevelt's Strategic Dilemma<br />Chapter 30: Japan's Defeat in the South<br />Chapter 31: Amphibious Battle: Okinawa<br />Chapter 32: Super-Weapons and the Defeat of Japan<br />Chapter 33: The Legacy of the Second World War<br /></span>
