              <span id="reviewTextContainer2409147967" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11591307239465981975">Wow! This was not the book I had in mind for learning more about WWII. For some reason I thought it was 150 pages, not 600. However, I muddled through and sometimes skimmed a bit. There was far more detail than I was even interested in but occasionally that was good as I learned quite a bit. In the end I was astonished that any writer would undertake such a task. Just a bit of heavy reading to start the summer. Now on to lighter things ....</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

