        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2094334225" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1968680251068388259">This book is not so much about what happened in the Second World War (though that&apos;s also part of it) as rather why it happened. The factors building up to from before the First World War, but also what decisions, good and bad, affected the outcome. <br/><br/>Very much recommended to any student of those times.</span>
  <span id="freeText1968680251068388259" style="display:none">This book is not so much about what happened in the Second World War (though that's also part of it) as rather why it happened. The factors building up to from before the First World War, but also what decisions, good and bad, affected the outcome. <br /><br />Very much recommended to any student of those times.</span>
