          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/4619485.John_Keegan"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1332081125p3/4619485.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/4619485.John_Keegan">John Keegan
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
575
followers
</div>

</div>
