<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer18042897544213550546">Sir John Desmond Patrick Keegan, OBE, FRSL was a British military historian, lecturer and journalist. He published many works on the nature of combat between the 14th and 21st centuries concerning land, air, maritime and intelligence warfare as well as the psychology of battle. </span>

</div>
</div>

